-------------------------------------------------------------------

     =========================================================
     Geant4 - an Object-Oriented Toolkit for Simulation in HEP
     =========================================================

                            G4Moss

This program provides a Geant4-based method for Mossbauer Effect. Please
add the data base to your envirnment first. The code is not only include 
the recoilless absorption, but aslo simulates the after process including
inner conversion which emits the electron, and reemission gamma rays.

	
